  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): clarify your role — is this a game you built, or deep mods on an\n     existing one? It's your single biggest body of screenshot work (~340 shots\n     across your history), so it clearly matters. Add your voice. Draft. -->\n<p class=\"\">Deep work on Subway Builder — a transit-simulation game: designing train types with realistic acceleration, capacity, and cost parameters; laying networks over real-world geography; and building construction and analysis tooling. (Also spun off <code class=\"md-inline-code\">subway-builder-mods</code> and a Pico-8 demake.)</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Subway Builder construction mode — laying track in an isometric city\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1780066321/projects/subway-builder/build.png\" alt=\"Subway Builder construction mode — laying track in an isometric city\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1780066321/projects/subway-builder/build.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1780066321/projects/subway-builder/build.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1780066321/projects/subway-builder/build.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1780066321/projects/subway-builder/build.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Subway Builder construction mode — laying track in an isometric city\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"2560×1440\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-video w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Subway Builder construction mode — laying track in an isometric city</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"A subwa